    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a framework for authorization policies controlling access to application-specific data.  This framework combines common location- and presence-specific authorization aspects.  An XML schema specifies the language in which common policy rules are represented.  The common policy framework can be extended to other application domains. [STANDARDS-TRACK]</t>
